as also AdjI↓ 
and tdj-I↓ (Ṣ, Ḳ) 
and AidojawojaI↓: (Ḳ:) or, accord. to Aṣ, dajaA, said of the night, is not from the being dark, but signifies it covered everything: and hence, he says, the phrase, munocu dajaA AlUisolaAmu, meaning Since 
